Package: nmm-qt-client
Architecture: any
Depends: libnetmaumaucommon2 (>= 0.11~),
         libnetmaumauclient3 (>= 0.11~),
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: netmaumau-server
Description: Proof of concept Qt client for NetMauMau
 Qt4 proof of concept client for the NetMauMau server. It offers a complete 
 playable client for playing against other players or AI opponents over the
 network.
 It can start a local server if installed and supports a list of multiple
 servers.

